IDString "SMA"

Get JUNK Short
Get FILES Long
Get DIR_SIZE Long

For A = 0 < FILES
	Get LEN Byte
	GetDString FILENAME LEN
	Get SIZE Long
	Get ZSIZE Long
	Get OFFSET Long
	CLog FILENAME OFFSET ZSIZE SIZE
Next A

